# A2 double-derivation repro (verbatim from
# docs/proposals/StackSafeNegation.checkpoint-c-notes.md "Double-derivation
# repro"). Seed makes t(1,3) double-derived -- base edge(1,3) AND recursive
# t(1,2),edge(2,3). The batch removes BOTH supports; expected final
# t = {(1,2)}.
batch
+ edge_msg 1 2
+ edge_msg 2 3
+ edge_msg 1 3
end
batch
- edge_msg 1 3
- edge_msg 2 3
end
